data.description:
Welcome to 33773 Elk Run, a stunning Evergreen gem nestled amidst the breathtaking beauty of the Colorado mountains. This 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom acreage property offers the perfect blend of modern amenities, mountain charm, and serene privacy for home buyers, families, and those seeking a vacation retreat. **New Roof Installed September 2023**

Set on just over one acre of land, this picturesque home boasts amazing panoramic views of Shadow Mountain and the Arapaho National Forest. Soak in the scenery from multiple newly re-stained/painted decks (2023), or gaze upon it through expansive windows throughout the house. The southern-facing exposure allows for an abundance of natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.

Inside, the home has been meticulously updated, featuring a chef's kitchen equipped with top-end Samsung black stainless-steel appliances (new in 2023), a touchless faucet, farmhouse sink, five kick plate drawers, a large pantry, and soft-closing cabinet doors. Vaulted ceilings evoke the quintessential mountain home feel, while a custom fireplace with a reclaimed wood mantel serves as the living room's centerpiece.

Additional features include new exterior paint/solid stain in 2020, new paint/solid stain on all of the decks (2023), entire property recently fire mitigated (2023), built in surround sound speakers in the media room, a mini-split AC/heat system with room for expansion (2021), a newer water heater (2021), a new garage door with battery backup (2023), 1GB internet availability from Comcast, a Google Nest Security System, custom window treatments and a fenced backyard with a large breed electric dog fence. 

33773 Elk Run is the ideal sanctuary for those who crave the Colorado mountain lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to make this spectacular property your own.
